891
01:12:11,920 --> 01:12:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] To sam ja i Apple, zar ne?

892
01:12:13,119 --> 01:12:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam veliki obožavatelj Applea.

893
01:12:15,119 --> 01:12:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] Sad nisam obožavatelj Applea.

894
01:12:16,720 --> 01:12:17,520
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam neprijatelj Applea.

895
01:12:17,600 --> 01:12:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je samo kao da je to moj posao, zar ne?

896
01:12:18,960 --> 01:12:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad je u pitanju ovo, postoji dio toga.

897
01:12:20,800 --> 01:12:29,119
