906
01:13:07,920 --> 01:13:08,640
[SPEAKER_01] To je sjajno.

907
01:13:08,880 --> 01:13:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako sjajno što se to dogodilo.

908
01:13:10,479 --> 01:13:18,159
