912
01:13:25,359 --> 01:13:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] I opet, volim trgovinu aplikacijama.

913
01:13:27,520 --> 01:13:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je sjajno.

914
01:13:28,239 --> 01:13:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] Stvorila je toliko prilika.

915
01:13:30,239 --> 01:13:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] I ja dolazim do toga.

916
01:13:32,319 --> 01:13:33,600
