921
01:13:44,560 --> 01:13:50,640
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno me muče prepreke i troškovi koje to stvara malom momku, zar ne?

922
01:13:50,880 --> 01:13:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] Velike tvrtke mogu se nositi s tom složenosti.

923
01:13:53,279 --> 01:13:55,359
